title: y is everyone so in love with me
lyrics:

Could it be my lips, or my energy? (Yee)
I could count 'em up, be like one, two, three (Woo)
Everybody act so in love with me
Why is everyone so in love with me? (Oh, babe)
Maybe it's my vibe, or your Hennessy (Woo)
I thought you would click, could you keep it G? (Woo)
Everybody act so in love with me
